race.comment: FULL HAO (9) deep into her prep and looking for the 2000m now. Back in trip when she attacked the line late for a narrow third over 1600m at this track. Drops further in weight for this and expect to see her race closer today. Can give this a great shake. DEAL N' DASH (17) staying gelding ready to produce at his third run in. Surged late from back in the field with a tidy third over 1600m here. Looks to have developed further this time in and can keep improving as he gets out to this trip and further. BELLA MONTAGNA (3) drifted back from the sticky draw and never really threatened when sixth over 1600m in the G3 Belle of the Turf Stakes at Gosford last Sunday. Placed at the trip and shapes as one of the leading chances. ECLAIR ENCORE (6) holding her form and due for a change of luck. Yet to be tested at the 2000m and will relish the weight drop with Osmond's claim. No surprise to see her in the finish.
